800
00:33:36,792 --> 00:33:39,041
For 50 years,
this woman took care of me,

801
00:33:39,083 --> 00:33:41,375
and then suddenly...

802
00:33:43,125 --> 00:33:47,333
Anyway, I, uh...

803
00:33:47,375 --> 00:33:48,625
I called Jimmy,

804
00:33:48,667 --> 00:33:53,125
