830
00:35:09,083 --> 00:35:10,083
What are you talking about?

831
00:35:10,125 --> 00:35:11,959
Sam and Jake outed you.

832
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:13,458
I have to admit,
I thought it was a little odd

833
00:35:13,500 --> 00:35:14,750
