00:36:53,500 --> 00:36:54,792
Okay.

862
00:36:54,834 --> 00:36:56,458
I swear to god,
if you sing, i--
Charlotte.

863
00:37:03,625 --> 00:37:06,000
Hi.

864
00:37:06,041 --> 00:37:07,792
I cannot wait
to meet you guys.

865
00:37:07,834 --> 00:37:11,792
Know that your dad will always
be there for you no matter what

