883
00:37:48,709 --> 00:37:50,917
♪♪♪

884
00:37:50,959 --> 00:37:52,667
Hey. Hey. Hey.

885
00:37:52,709 --> 00:37:54,875
I... I like you.

886
00:37:54,917 --> 00:37:57,041
Okay?

887
00:37:57,083 --> 00:37:59,750
I like you.

