00:38:04,250 --> 00:38:08,041
♪ came in
from a rainy Thursday ♪

889
00:38:08,083 --> 00:38:11,625
♪ on the Avenue ♪

890
00:38:11,667 --> 00:38:15,166
♪ I thought I heard
you talking softly ♪

891
00:38:15,208 --> 00:38:18,041
I'd like to talk now.

892
00:38:18,083 --> 00:38:19,709
Can we do that?

893
00:38:19,750 --> 00:38:22,792
♪ I turned on the lights,
the TV ♪

894
00:38:22,834 --> 00:38:26,583
♪ and the radio ♪

895
00:38:26,625 --> 00:38:29,000
I loved Mark Sloan.

