929
00:39:58,709 --> 00:40:04,041
The third thing I want to say
is that, uh...

930
00:40:05,750 --> 00:40:07,583
I'm sorry.

931
00:40:07,625 --> 00:40:10,000
You're sorry?

932
00:40:10,041 --> 00:40:12,792
A man you loved...

933
00:40:12,834 --> 00:40:14,083
Died.

934
00:40:14,125 --> 00:40:16,458
♪♪♪

